  "reference_number": "RUS1706",
  "remarks": "\nEvgeny Mikhailovich SHKOLOV is an involved person within the meaning of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because he is working as the Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors for JSC System Operator of the Unified Energy System (SO UES), which is carrying on business in the energy sector, a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, and is therefore involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
